query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('mathematica')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('bugs',
'calculus-and-analysis',
'equation-solving',
'functions',
'graphs-and-networks',
'numerics',
'performance-tuning',
'plotting',
'simplifying-expressions');
